<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">人生之路，亦如八一建军之路，有坦途也有陡坡，有平川也有险途，有直道也有弯路。我们只有在青春的时候奋斗，才能让青春的枝头绽放理想之花，让理想奔赴实际。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240418/1713445908605091186.png" title="1713445908605091186.png" alt="image.png" width="309" height="259" style="width: 309px; height: 259px;"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240418/1713445871916021368.png" title="1713445871916021368.png" alt="image.png" width="429" height="262" style="width: 429px; height: 262px;"/></span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"><br/></span></p>